    "body": "Our current validator client implementation does not guarantee that the aggregation step happens strictly after publishing the attestation\r\n\r\nIf this API call is significantly delayed\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/ea5e141daebce417f92f58520f7ea5741ce9a4e0/packages/validator/src/services/attestation.ts#L220\r\n\r\nThe timeout wrapping this call will fire and may be executed before completing the above if the beacon node is overloaded\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/ea5e141daebce417f92f58520f7ea5741ce9a4e0/packages/validator/src/services/attestation.ts#L212\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\nFull relevant code\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/ea5e141daebce417f92f58520f7ea5741ce9a4e0/packages/validator/src/services/attestation.ts#L199-L224",
